reviewText: I was expecting more a detail description of birds with some kind of menu to check birds but is just a plain video talking about places and some birds stories. No bad but not good at all

Often photographing nature in Florida,I was anxious to see this DVD.I expected to see a parade of beautiful birds,but received much more. Messineo's exceptional images were accompanied by interesting and humorous stories of birds in their special habitats--The stories were delightful and educational---and the narrative first class,deserving high praise. Cosmas Liu,M.D.
Absolutely gorgeous imagery and spectacularly witty and original narration. A must have for nature lovers and wouldbe photographers alike!
